		<summary lang="en_GB">A skin that turns Kodi into a simple weather clock</summary>
		<description lang="en_GB">Inspired by Estouchy, a skin designed to be used on a touchscreen device like the Raspberry Pi with touchscreen that converts Kodi into a simple weather clock.</description>
